OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,FAs she prepares to attend another
OL,7,Fparole hearing for one of her son's
OL,8,Fkillers Jon Venables, Denise Fergus
OL,9,Fsays offenders who breach the terms of
OL,10,Ftheir licence should stay in prison as
OL,11,FAndy Bonner reports.
OL,13,FThe mother of James Bulger is calling
OL,14,Ffor criminals who breach the terms of
OL,15,Ftheir licence too many times to lose
OL,16,Ftheir right to parole.
OL,18,FDenise Fergus is preparing to attend
OL,19,Fanother parole hearing for one of her
OL,20,Fson's killers, Jon Venables.
