OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,FThe murder of James Bulger in
OL,7,FMerseyside in 1993 made headlines
OL,8,Faround the world.
OL,10,FThe toddler was kidnapped, from a
OL,11,Fshopping centre in Bootle, and
OL,12,Ftortured by two 10 year old boys.
OL,14,FJon Venables and Robert Thompson were
OL,15,Freleased on license with new
OL,16,Fidentities, after serving eight years
OL,17,Fin secure youth accommodation. and the
OL,18,Fsubsequent release of his two killers
OL,19,Fwhen they turned 18 angered many.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
