OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,FDenise says: "I said years ago, when
OL,7,FJames was first taken from me, that,
OL,8,Fbecause they weren't properly punished
OL,9,Ffor the crime that they committed,
OL,10,Fthey're definitely going to go on to
OL,11,Fre-offend that we definitely know one
OL,12,Fhas, not just once but twice.
OL,14,F"He's been caught with drugs, so I
OL,15,Fdon't know why he wasn't taken into
OL,16,Fprison for that.
OL,18,F"He was entering Merseyside, he was
OL,19,Fgoing to Everton Games, which is not
OL,20,Ffar from where I live, He's just
OL,21,Fbroken all rules."
