OL,6,FIt was when indecent images of
OL,7,Fchildren were found on Venables'
OL,8,Fcomputer that he was twice recalled to
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FNow, James's mother is preparing for
OL,12,Fanother parole hearing, where his
OL,13,Fanonymity would be protected.
OL,15,FShe said: "It's really annoying, he's
OL,16,Fprobably knowing everything about me,
OL,17,Fhe probably knows everything about my
OL,18,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
