OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,F"We get to know nothing about him,
OL,7,Fnothing at all, everything is kept
OL,8,Fquiet on him.
OL,10,F But I'm having to fight justice for
OL,11,FJames, I'm having to do that, because
OL,12,Fof what he's done.
OL,14,FDenise told Good Morning Britain she
OL,15,Ffinds parole hearings mentally
OL,16,Fdraining, but it's something she needs
OL,17,Fto be a part of.
