OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,FShe said. "I've been living a life of
OL,7,Fa nightmare, but, you know, at the end
OL,8,Fof the day, when there's no fight
OL,9,Fthere, I go back to being a mum and a
OL,10,Fwife, which is what I love doing.
OL,12,F"That's the job that I prefer to do
OL,13,Fbut, you know, when something like
OL,14,Fthis comes off, I've got to stand up
OL,15,Fand, start fighting again."
OL,17,FDenise Fergus wants the law to change
OL,18,Fso that breaches of parole means no
OL,19,Fmore chances.
