OL,3,CJames Bulger's Mum hopes son's killer
OL,4,C'never sees the light of day'
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Lord Chancellor now has the
OL,8,Fpower to refer certain release
OL,9,Fdecisions for the most serious
OL,10,Foffenders to the High Court for a
OL,11,Fsecond check. "
OL,13,FDenise says: "I'm just hoping and
OL,14,Fpraying that they do take into
OL,15,Fconsideration everything that he's
OL,16,Fdone, murdering James, and whatever
OL,17,Fhe's done after that and I'm hoping
OL,18,Fthat they realise that he is still a
OL,19,Fhigh risk to other kids.
